{
  "video_id": "PLXsUgL_wpc",
  "title": "Newton Aduaka: The story of Ezra, a child soldier",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12160.0,
      "end_time": 15160.0,
      "text": "This is very strange for me, because I’m not used to doing this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15160.0,
      "end_time": 18160.0,
      "text": "I usually stand on the other side of the light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18160.0,
      "end_time": 25160.0,
      "text": "and now I&#39;m feeling the pressure I put other people into. And it&#39;s hard ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25160.0,
      "end_time": 28160.0,
      "text": "The previous speaker has, I think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28160.0,
      "end_time": 34160.0,
      "text": "really painted a very good background as to"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 34160.0,
      "end_time": 40160.0,
      "text": "the impulse behind my work and what drives me, and my sense of loss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 40160.0,
      "end_time": 46160.0,
      "text": "and trying to find the answer to the big questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 46160.0,
      "end_time": 51160.0,
      "text": "But this, for me, I mean, coming here to do this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 51160.0,
      "end_time": 59160.0,
      "text": "feels like -- there’s this sculptor that I like very much, Giacometti,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 59160.0,
      "end_time": 64160.0,
      "text": "who after many years of living in France -- and learning, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 64160.0,
      "end_time": 71160.0,
      "text": "studying and working -- he returned home and he was asked, what did you produce?"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 71160.0,
      "end_time": 75160.0,
      "text": "What have you done with so many years of being away?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 75160.0,
      "end_time": 78160.0,
      "text": "And he sort of, he showed a handful of figurines."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 78160.0,
      "end_time": 83160.0,
      "text": "And obviously they were, \"Is this what you spent years doing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 83160.0,
      "end_time": 88160.0,
      "text": "And we expected huge masterpieces!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 88160.0,
      "end_time": 94160.0,
      "text": "But what struck me is the understanding that in those little pieces"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 94160.0,
      "end_time": 100160.0,
      "text": "was the culmination of a man’s life, search, thought, everything --"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 100160.0,
      "end_time": 102160.0,
      "text": "just in a reduced, small version."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 102160.0,
      "end_time": 104160.0,
      "text": "In a way, I feel like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 104160.0,
      "end_time": 107160.0,
      "text": "I feel like I’m coming home to talk about"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 107160.0,
      "end_time": 111160.0,
      "text": "what I’ve been away doing for 20 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 111160.0,
      "end_time": 117160.0,
      "text": "And I will start with a brief taster of what I’ve been about:"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 117160.0,
      "end_time": 119160.0,
      "text": "a handful of films -- nothing much,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 119160.0,
      "end_time": 122160.0,
      "text": "two feature films and a handful of short films."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 122160.0,
      "end_time": 126160.0,
      "text": "So, we’ll go with the first piece."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 126160.0,
      "end_time": 135160.0,
      "text": "(Video) Woman: \"I destroy lives,\" mum said."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 135160.0,
      "end_time": 137160.0,
      "text": "I love her, you know."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 139160.0,
      "end_time": 141160.0,
      "text": "She’s not even my real mum."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 141160.0,
      "end_time": 145160.0,
      "text": "My real mum and dad dumped me"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 145160.0,
      "end_time": 147160.0,
      "text": "and fucked off back to Nigeria."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 152160.0,
      "end_time": 156160.0,
      "text": "The devil is in me, Court."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 156160.0,
      "end_time": 158160.0,
      "text": "Court: Sleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 160160.0,
      "end_time": 162160.0,
      "text": "Woman: Have you ever been?"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 162160.0,
      "end_time": 164160.0,
      "text": "Court: Where?"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 164160.0,
      "end_time": 166160.0,
      "text": "Woman: Nigeria."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 168160.0,
      "end_time": 170160.0,
      "text": "Court: Never."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 170160.0,
      "end_time": 173160.0,
      "text": "My mum wanted to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 173160.0,
      "end_time": 175160.0,
      "text": "couldn’t afford it."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 176160.0,
      "end_time": 178160.0,
      "text": "Woman: Wish I could."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 178160.0,
      "end_time": 181160.0,
      "text": "I have this feeling I’d be happy there."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 188160.0,
      "end_time": 190160.0,
      "text": "Why does everyone get rid of me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 192160.0,
      "end_time": 194160.0,
      "text": "Court: I don&#39;t want to get rid of you."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 194160.0,
      "end_time": 198160.0,
      "text": "Woman: You don&#39;t need me."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 198160.0,
      "end_time": 201160.0,
      "text": "You’re just too blind to see it now."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 203160.0,
      "end_time": 206160.0,
      "text": "Boy: What do you do all day?"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 207160.0,
      "end_time": 209160.0,
      "text": "Marcus: Read."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 209160.0,
      "end_time": 211160.0,
      "text": "Boy: Don&#39;t you get bored?"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 211160.0,
      "end_time": 214160.0,
      "text": "And how come you ain&#39;t got a job anyway?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 214160.0,
      "end_time": 216160.0,
      "text": "Marcus: I am retired."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 216160.0,
      "end_time": 218160.0,
      "text": "Boy: So?"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 218160.0,
      "end_time": 221160.0,
      "text": "Marcus: So I&#39;ve done my bit for Queen and country, now I work for myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 221160.0,
      "end_time": 223160.0,
      "text": "Boy: No, now you sit around like a bum all day."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 223160.0,
      "end_time": 226160.0,
      "text": "Marcus: Because I do what I like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 226160.0,
      "end_time": 228160.0,
      "text": "Boy: Look man, reading don&#39;t feed no one."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 228160.0,
      "end_time": 230160.0,
      "text": "And it particularly don&#39;t feed your spliff habit."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 230160.0,
      "end_time": 234160.0,
      "text": "Marcus: It feeds my mind and my soul."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 234160.0,
      "end_time": 241160.0,
      "text": "Boy: Arguing with you is a waste of time, Marcus."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 241160.0,
      "end_time": 243160.0,
      "text": "Marcus: You’re a rapper, am I right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 243160.0,
      "end_time": 244160.0,
      "text": "Boy: Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 244160.0,
      "end_time": 245160.0,
      "text": "Marcus: A modern day poet."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 245160.0,
      "end_time": 246160.0,
      "text": "Boy: Yeah, you could say that."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 246160.0,
      "end_time": 248160.0,
      "text": "Marcus: So what do you talk about?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 248160.0,
      "end_time": 250160.0,
      "text": "Boy: What&#39;s that supposed to mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 250160.0,
      "end_time": 252160.0,
      "text": "Marcus: Simple. What do you rap about?"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 252160.0,
      "end_time": 254160.0,
      "text": "Boy: Reality, man."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 254160.0,
      "end_time": 255160.0,
      "text": "Marcus: Whose reality?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 255160.0,
      "end_time": 257159.0,
      "text": "Boy: My fuckin&#39; reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 257160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259160.00000000003,
      "text": "Marcus: Tell me about your reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 259160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263160.0,
      "text": "Boy: Racism, oppression, people like me not getting a break in life."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 263160.0,
      "end_time": 266160.0,
      "text": "Marcus: So what solutions do you offer? I mean, the job of a poet is not just --"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 266160.0,
      "end_time": 269160.0,
      "text": "Boy: Man, fight the power! Simple: blow the motherfuckers out of the sky."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 269160.0,
      "end_time": 270160.0,
      "text": "Marcus: With an AK-47?"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 270160.0,
      "end_time": 272160.0,
      "text": "Boy: Man, if I had one, too fuckin&#39; right."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 272160.0,
      "end_time": 275160.0,
      "text": "Marcus: And how many soldiers have you recruited to fight this war with you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 275160.0,
      "end_time": 278160.0,
      "text": "Boy: Oh, Marcus, you know what I mean."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 278160.0,
      "end_time": 280160.0,
      "text": "Marcus: When a man resorts to profanities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 280160.0,
      "end_time": 284160.0,
      "text": "it’s a sure sign of his inability to express himself."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 284160.0,
      "end_time": 287160.0,
      "text": "Boy: See man, you’re just taking the piss out of me now."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 287160.0,
      "end_time": 289160.0,
      "text": "Marcus: The Panthers."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 289160.0,
      "end_time": 290160.0,
      "text": "Boy: Panthers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 290160.0,
      "end_time": 294160.0,
      "text": "Ass kickin&#39; guys who were fed up with all that white supremacist, powers-that-be bullshit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 294160.0,
      "end_time": 297160.0,
      "text": "and just went in there and kicked everybody&#39;s arse."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 297160.0,
      "end_time": 301160.0,
      "text": "Fuckin’ wicked, man. I saw the movie. Bad! What?"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 301160.0,
      "end_time": 305160.0,
      "text": "Director 1: I saw his last film."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 305160.0,
      "end_time": 307160.0,
      "text": "Épuise, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 307160.0,
      "end_time": 308160.0,
      "text": "Woman 1: Yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 308160.0,
      "end_time": 315160.0,
      "text": "D1: Not to make a bad joke, but it was really épuisé."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 315160.0,
      "end_time": 322160.0,
      "text": "Epuisé -- tired, exhausted, fed up."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 322160.0,
      "end_time": 324160.0,
      "text": "Director 2: Can you not shut up?"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 324160.0,
      "end_time": 326160.0,
      "text": "Now, you talk straight to me, what’s wrong with my films?"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 326160.0,
      "end_time": 328160.0,
      "text": "Let’s go."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 328160.0,
      "end_time": 329160.0,
      "text": "W1: They suck."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 329160.0,
      "end_time": 331160.0,
      "text": "Woman 2: They suck? What about yours?"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 332160.0,
      "end_time": 335160.0,
      "text": "What, what, what, what about, what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 335160.0,
      "end_time": 337160.0,
      "text": "What do you think about your movie?"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 337160.0,
      "end_time": 339160.0,
      "text": "D1: My movies, they are OK, fine."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 339160.0,
      "end_time": 342160.0,
      "text": "They are better than making documentaries no one ever sees."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 342160.0,
      "end_time": 344160.0,
      "text": "What the fuck are you talking about?"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 344160.0,
      "end_time": 347160.0,
      "text": "Did you ever move your fuckin&#39; ass from Hollywood"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 347160.0,
      "end_time": 349160.0,
      "text": "to go and film something real?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 349160.0,
      "end_time": 351160.0,
      "text": "You make people fuckin&#39; sleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 351160.0,
      "end_time": 353160.0,
      "text": "Dream about bullshit."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 353160.0,
      "end_time": 357160.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 357160.0,
      "end_time": 362160.0,
      "text": "Newton Aduaka: Thank you. The first clip, really, is"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 362160.0,
      "end_time": 366160.0,
      "text": "totally trying to capture what cinema is for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 366160.0,
      "end_time": 368160.0,
      "text": "and where I&#39;m coming from in terms of cinema."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 368160.0,
      "end_time": 373160.0,
      "text": "The first piece was, really, there&#39;s a young woman talking about Nigeria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 373160.0,
      "end_time": 376160.0,
      "text": "that she has a feeling she&#39;ll be happy there."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 376160.0,
      "end_time": 379160.0,
      "text": "These are the sentiments of someone that&#39;s been away from home."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 379160.0,
      "end_time": 382160.0,
      "text": "And that was something that I went through, you know, and I&#39;m still going through."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 382160.0,
      "end_time": 385160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve not been home for quite a while, for about five years now."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 385160.0,
      "end_time": 387160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been away 20 years in total."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 389160.0,
      "end_time": 392160.0,
      "text": "And so it’s really --"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 392160.0,
      "end_time": 398160.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s really how suddenly, you know, this was made in 1997,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 398160.0,
      "end_time": 402160.0,
      "text": "which is the time of Abacha -- the military dictatorship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 402160.0,
      "end_time": 407160.0,
      "text": "the worst part of Nigerian history, this post-colonial history."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 407160.0,
      "end_time": 409160.0,
      "text": "So, for this girl to have these dreams"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 409160.0,
      "end_time": 413160.0,
      "text": "is simply how we preserve a sense of what home is."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 413160.0,
      "end_time": 419160.0,
      "text": "How -- and it&#39;s sort of, perhaps romantic, but I think beautiful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 419160.0,
      "end_time": 423160.0,
      "text": "because you just need something to hold on to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 423160.0,
      "end_time": 426160.0,
      "text": "especially in a society where you feel alienated."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 426160.0,
      "end_time": 429160.0,
      "text": "Which takes us to the next piece, where the young man"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 429160.0,
      "end_time": 435160.0,
      "text": "talks about lack of opportunity: living as a black person in Europe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 435160.0,
      "end_time": 439160.0,
      "text": "the glass ceiling that we all know about, that we all talk about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 439160.0,
      "end_time": 443160.0,
      "text": "and his reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 443160.0,
      "end_time": 445160.0,
      "text": "Again, this was my -- this was me talking about --"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 445160.0,
      "end_time": 449160.0,
      "text": "this was, again, the time of multiculturalism in the United Kingdom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 449160.0,
      "end_time": 452160.0,
      "text": "and there was this buzzword -- and it was trying to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 452160.0,
      "end_time": 456160.0,
      "text": "what exactly does this multiculturalism mean in the real lives of people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 456160.0,
      "end_time": 459160.0,
      "text": "And what would a child --"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 459160.0,
      "end_time": 462160.0,
      "text": "what does a child like Jamie -- the young boy -- think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 462160.0,
      "end_time": 466160.0,
      "text": "I mean, with all this anger that&#39;s built up inside of him?"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 466160.0,
      "end_time": 468160.0,
      "text": "What happens with that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 468160.0,
      "end_time": 470160.0,
      "text": "What, of course, happens with that is violence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 470160.0,
      "end_time": 474160.0,
      "text": "which we see when we talk about the ghettos"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 474160.0,
      "end_time": 478160.0,
      "text": "and we talk about, you know, South Central L.A. and this kind of stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 478160.0,
      "end_time": 481160.0,
      "text": "and which eventually, when channeled, becomes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 481160.0,
      "end_time": 486160.0,
      "text": "you know, evolves and manifests itself as riots --"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 486160.0,
      "end_time": 490160.0,
      "text": "like the one in France two years ago, where I live,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 490160.0,
      "end_time": 492160.0,
      "text": "which shocked everybody, because everyone thought, \"Oh well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 492160.0,
      "end_time": 494160.0,
      "text": "France is a liberal society.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 494160.0,
      "end_time": 497160.0,
      "text": "But I lived in England for 18 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 497160.0,
      "end_time": 500160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve lived in France for about four, and I feel actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 500160.0,
      "end_time": 505160.0,
      "text": "thrown back 20 years, living in France."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 505160.0,
      "end_time": 508160.0,
      "text": "And then, the third piece. The third piece for me is the question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 508160.0,
      "end_time": 511160.0,
      "text": "What is cinema to you? What do you do with cinema?"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 511160.0,
      "end_time": 519160.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a young director, Hollywood director, with his friends --"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 519159.0,
      "end_time": 522159.0,
      "text": "fellow filmmakers -- talking about what cinema means."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 522159.0,
      "end_time": 526160.0,
      "text": "I suppose that will take me to my last piece --"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 526160.0,
      "end_time": 528160.0,
      "text": "what cinema means for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 528160.0,
      "end_time": 532160.0,
      "text": "My life started as a -- I started life in 1966,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 532160.0,
      "end_time": 535160.0,
      "text": "a few months before the Biafran, which lasted for three years"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 535160.0,
      "end_time": 537160.0,
      "text": "and it was three years of war."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 537160.0,
      "end_time": 540160.0,
      "text": "So that whole thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 540160.0,
      "end_time": 546160.0,
      "text": "that whole childhood echoes and takes me into the next piece."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 556160.0,
      "end_time": 559160.0,
      "text": "(Video) Voice: Onicha, off to school with your brother."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 559160.0,
      "end_time": 561160.0,
      "text": "Onicha: Yes, mama."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 609160.0,
      "end_time": 616160.0,
      "text": "Commander: Soldiers, you are going to fight a battle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 616160.0,
      "end_time": 619160.0,
      "text": "so you must get ready and willing to die."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 619160.0,
      "end_time": 620160.0,
      "text": "You must get -- ?"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 620160.0,
      "end_time": 623160.0,
      "text": "Child Soldiers: Ready and willing to die."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 623160.0,
      "end_time": 629160.0,
      "text": "C: Success, the change is only coming through the barrel of the gun."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 629160.0,
      "end_time": 631160.0,
      "text": "CS: The barrel of the gun!"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 631160.0,
      "end_time": 632160.0,
      "text": "C: This is the gun."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 632160.0,
      "end_time": 636160.0,
      "text": "CS: This is the gun."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 636160.0,
      "end_time": 638160.0,
      "text": "C: This is an AK-47 rifle. This is your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 638160.0,
      "end_time": 644160.0,
      "text": "This is your life. This is ... this is ... this is your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 644160.0,
      "end_time": 647160.0,
      "text": "Ezra: They give us the special drugs. We call it bubbles."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 647160.0,
      "end_time": 649160.0,
      "text": "Amphetamines."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 650160.0,
      "end_time": 653160.0,
      "text": "Soldiers: Rain come, sun come, soldier man dey go."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 653160.0,
      "end_time": 656160.0,
      "text": "I say rain come, sun come, soldier man dey go."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 656160.0,
      "end_time": 658160.0,
      "text": "We went from one village to another -- three villages."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 658160.0,
      "end_time": 660160.0,
      "text": "I don’t remember how we got there."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 660160.0,
      "end_time": 663160.0,
      "text": "Witness: We walked and walked for two days."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 663160.0,
      "end_time": 665160.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t eat."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 665160.0,
      "end_time": 669160.0,
      "text": "There was no food, just little rice."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 669160.0,
      "end_time": 671160.0,
      "text": "Without food -- I was sick."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 671160.0,
      "end_time": 674160.0,
      "text": "The injection made us not to have mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 674160.0,
      "end_time": 676160.0,
      "text": "God will forgive us."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 676160.0,
      "end_time": 679160.0,
      "text": "He knows we did not know. We did not know!"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 695160.0,
      "end_time": 698160.0,
      "text": "Committee Chairman: Do you remember January 6th, 1999?"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 700160.0,
      "end_time": 702160.0,
      "text": "Ezra: I don’t remember."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 702160.0,
      "end_time": 705160.0,
      "text": "Various Voices: You will die! You will die! (Screaming)"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 705160.0,
      "end_time": 707160.0,
      "text": "Onicha: Ezra! (Ezra: Onicha! Onicha!)"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 707160.0,
      "end_time": 715160.0,
      "text": "Various Voices: ♫ We don&#39;t need no more trouble ♫"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 715160.0,
      "end_time": 717160.0,
      "text": "♫ No more trouble ♫"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 717160.0,
      "end_time": 719160.0,
      "text": "They killed my mother."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 719160.0,
      "end_time": 721160.0,
      "text": "The Mende sons of bastards."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 721160.0,
      "end_time": 723160.0,
      "text": "(Shouting)"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 724160.0,
      "end_time": 726160.0,
      "text": "Who is she?"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 726160.0,
      "end_time": 727160.0,
      "text": "Me."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 727160.0,
      "end_time": 728160.0,
      "text": "Why you giving these to me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 728160.0,
      "end_time": 730160.0,
      "text": "So you can stop staring at me."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 731160.0,
      "end_time": 734160.0,
      "text": "My story is a little bit complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 734160.0,
      "end_time": 736160.0,
      "text": "I’m interested."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 736160.0,
      "end_time": 738160.0,
      "text": "Mariam is pregnant."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 738160.0,
      "end_time": 740160.0,
      "text": "You know what you are? A crocodile."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 740160.0,
      "end_time": 742160.0,
      "text": "Big mouth. Short legs."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 745160.0,
      "end_time": 747160.0,
      "text": "In front of Rufus you are Ezra the coward."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 747160.0,
      "end_time": 749160.0,
      "text": "He’s not taking care of his troops."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 749160.0,
      "end_time": 754160.0,
      "text": "Troop, pay your last honor. Salute."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 754160.0,
      "end_time": 756160.0,
      "text": "Open your eyes, Ezra."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 756160.0,
      "end_time": 758160.0,
      "text": "A blind man can see that the diamonds end up in his pocket."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 758160.0,
      "end_time": 766160.0,
      "text": "♫ We don&#39;t need no more trouble ♫"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 767160.0,
      "end_time": 769160.0,
      "text": "Get that idiot out!"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 770160.0,
      "end_time": 773160.0,
      "text": "I take you are preparing a major attack?"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 773160.0,
      "end_time": 774160.0,
      "text": "This must be the mine."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 775160.0,
      "end_time": 776160.0,
      "text": "Your girl is here."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 776160.0,
      "end_time": 780160.0,
      "text": "Well done, well done."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 781160.0,
      "end_time": 783160.0,
      "text": "That is what you are here for, no?"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 783160.0,
      "end_time": 786160.0,
      "text": "You are planning to go back to fight are you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 786160.0,
      "end_time": 793160.0,
      "text": "♫ We don&#39;t need no more trouble ♫"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 793160.0,
      "end_time": 795160.0,
      "text": "♫ No more trouble ♫"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 795160.0,
      "end_time": 805160.0,
      "text": "♫ We don&#39;t need no more trouble ♫"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 805160.0,
      "end_time": 808160.0,
      "text": "♫ No more trouble. ♫"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 808160.0,
      "end_time": 811160.0,
      "text": "Wake up! Everybody wake up. Road block!"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 811160.0,
      "end_time": 814160.0,
      "text": "♫ We don&#39;t need no more ... ♫"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 840160.0,
      "end_time": 845160.0,
      "text": "Committee Chairman: We hope that, with your help and the help of others, that this commission"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 845160.0,
      "end_time": 850160.0,
      "text": "will go a long way towards understanding the causes of the rebel war."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 850160.0,
      "end_time": 852160.0,
      "text": "More than that, begin a healing process and finally to --"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 852160.0,
      "end_time": 858160.0,
      "text": "as an act of closure to a terrible period in this country’s history."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 858160.0,
      "end_time": 859160.0,
      "text": "The beginning of hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 859160.0,
      "end_time": 863160.0,
      "text": "Mr. Ezra Gelehun, please stand."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 871160.0,
      "end_time": 876160.0,
      "text": "State your name and age for the commission."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 876160.0,
      "end_time": 878160.0,
      "text": "Ezra: My name is Ezra Gelehun."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 878160.0,
      "end_time": 882160.0,
      "text": "I am 15 or 16. I don’t remember."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 882160.0,
      "end_time": 887160.0,
      "text": "Ask my sister, she is the witch, she knows everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 887160.0,
      "end_time": 892160.0,
      "text": "(Sister: 16.)"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 892160.0,
      "end_time": 895160.0,
      "text": "CC: Mr. Gelehun, I’d like to remind you you’re not on trial here"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 895160.0,
      "end_time": 897160.0,
      "text": "for any crimes you committed."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 897160.0,
      "end_time": 899160.0,
      "text": "E: We were fighting for our freedom."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 899160.0,
      "end_time": 902160.0,
      "text": "If killing in a war is a crime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 902160.0,
      "end_time": 906160.0,
      "text": "then you have to charge every soldier in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 906160.0,
      "end_time": 910160.0,
      "text": "War is a crime, yes, but I did not start it."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 910160.0,
      "end_time": 914160.0,
      "text": "You too are a retired General, not so?"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 914160.0,
      "end_time": 916160.0,
      "text": "CC: Yes, correct."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 916160.0,
      "end_time": 918160.0,
      "text": "E: So you too must stand trial then."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 918160.0,
      "end_time": 922160.0,
      "text": "Our government was corrupt."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 922160.0,
      "end_time": 927160.0,
      "text": "Lack of education was their way to control power."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 927160.0,
      "end_time": 930160.0,
      "text": "If I may ask, do you pay for school in your country?"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 930160.0,
      "end_time": 935160.0,
      "text": "CC: No, we don’t."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 935160.0,
      "end_time": 937160.0,
      "text": "E: You are richer than us."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 937160.0,
      "end_time": 940160.0,
      "text": "But we pay for school."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 941160.0,
      "end_time": 943160.0,
      "text": "Your country talks about democracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 943160.0,
      "end_time": 947160.0,
      "text": "but you support corrupt governments like my own."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 947160.0,
      "end_time": 950160.0,
      "text": "Why? Because you want our diamond."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 950160.0,
      "end_time": 954160.0,
      "text": "Ask if anyone in this room have ever seen real diamond before?"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 954160.0,
      "end_time": 956160.0,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 956160.0,
      "end_time": 962160.0,
      "text": "CC: Mr. Gelehun, I&#39;d like to remind you, you&#39;re not on trial here today."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 962160.0,
      "end_time": 963160.0,
      "text": "You are not on trial."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 963160.0,
      "end_time": 966160.0,
      "text": "E: Then let me go."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 966160.0,
      "end_time": 969160.0,
      "text": "CC: I can&#39;t do that, son."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 969160.0,
      "end_time": 971160.0,
      "text": "E: So you are a liar."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 971160.0,
      "end_time": 973160.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 973160.0,
      "end_time": 976160.0,
      "text": "NA: Thank you. Just very quickly to say that my point really here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 976160.0,
      "end_time": 978160.0,
      "text": "is that while we’re making all these huge advancements,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 978160.0,
      "end_time": 984160.0,
      "text": "what we&#39;re doing, which for me, you know, I think we should --"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 984160.0,
      "end_time": 988160.0,
      "text": "Africa should move forward, but we should remember,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 988160.0,
      "end_time": 990160.0,
      "text": "so we do not go back here again."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 990160.0,
      "end_time": 991160.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 991160.0,
      "end_time": 993160.0,
      "text": "Emeka Okafor: Thank you, Newton."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 993160.0,
      "end_time": 996160.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 996160.0,
      "end_time": 1000160.0,
      "text": "One of the themes that comes through very strongly"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 1000160.0,
      "end_time": 1010160.0,
      "text": "in the piece we just watched is this sense of the psychological trauma of the young"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 1010160.0,
      "end_time": 1015160.0,
      "text": "that have to play this role of being child soldiers."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 1015160.0,
      "end_time": 1019160.0,
      "text": "And considering where you are coming from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 1019160.0,
      "end_time": 1025159.0,
      "text": "and when we consider the extent to which it’s not taken as seriously"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 1025160.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1029160.0000000001,
      "text": "as it should be, what would you have to say about that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 1029160.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1032160.0000000001,
      "text": "NA: In the process of my research, I actually spent"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 1032160.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1035160.0000000001,
      "text": "a bit of time in Sierra Leone researching this."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 1035160.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1040160.0000000001,
      "text": "And I remember I met a lot of child soldiers --"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 1040160.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1044160.0000000001,
      "text": "ex-combatants, as they like to be called."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 1046160.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1051160.0,
      "text": "I met psychosocial workers who worked with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 1051160.0,
      "end_time": 1054160.0,
      "text": "I met psychiatrists who spent time with them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 1054160.0,
      "end_time": 1057160.0,
      "text": "aid workers, NGOs, the whole lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 1057160.0,
      "end_time": 1061160.0,
      "text": "But I remember on the flight back on my last trip,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 1061160.0,
      "end_time": 1065160.0,
      "text": "I remember breaking down in tears and thinking to myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 1065160.0,
      "end_time": 1071160.0,
      "text": "if any kid in the West, in the western world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 1071160.0,
      "end_time": 1076160.0,
      "text": "went through a day of what any of those kids have gone through,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 1076160.0,
      "end_time": 1082160.0,
      "text": "they will be in therapy for the rest of their natural lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 1082160.0,
      "end_time": 1087160.0,
      "text": "So for me, the thought that we have all these children --"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 1087160.0,
      "end_time": 1090160.0,
      "text": "it’s a generation, we have a whole generation of children --"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 1090160.0,
      "end_time": 1097160.0,
      "text": "who have been put through so much psychological trauma or damage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 1097160.0,
      "end_time": 1099160.0,
      "text": "and Africa has to live with that."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 1099160.0,
      "end_time": 1101160.0,
      "text": "But I’m just saying to factor that in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 1101160.0,
      "end_time": 1104160.0,
      "text": "factor that in with all this great advancement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 1104160.0,
      "end_time": 1106160.0,
      "text": "all this pronouncement of great achievement."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 1108160.0,
      "end_time": 1110160.0,
      "text": "That’s really my thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 1110160.0,
      "end_time": 1113160.0,
      "text": "EO: Well, we thank you again for coming to the TED stage."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 1113160.0,
      "end_time": 1115160.0,
      "text": "That was a very moving piece."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 1115160.0,
      "end_time": 1116160.0,
      "text": "NA: Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 1116160.0,
      "end_time": 1117160.0,
      "text": "EO: Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 1117160.0,
      "end_time": 1118160.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}